{"tid":1933771,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★2018年 post 集中bin c 區","createTime":"2020-03-19T13:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T09:11:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf546df2f7cc97438085f54f3dfa374884952d5","tid":1933771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"All in 700果d<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n納米樓必勝果d"},{"pid":"43b459a18fb225aff5d20a998b925b3498f4fe71","tid":1933771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bcb8617aabd92106e714723a70d7954101d7b3","tid":1933771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ea408b0668378e31a3d2def82bb1519e847c71","tid":1933771,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:18:32.000Z","msg":"你唔好咁啦 2020 了 <br />\n<br />\n比佢地冷靜下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff5402936f4559048619e5a5eb111b80af6ca10","tid":1933771,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"科技板塊絕對看好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他續指，年內恒指累升逾23%，就算單月內下跌2,000點亦不意外。<br />\n<br />\n他最看好科技板塊，尤其是騰訊、瑞聲科技(02018)和舜宇光學科技(02382)。他指，科技股增長動力強，且未來改變大眾生活毋庸置疑，故絕對看好。惟他提醒，一定要揀行業領頭羊。但騰訊本周三公布業績，不妨績後再作打算。<br />\n<br />\n他也看好滙豐控股(00005)，指該股業績表現理想兼有回購支持，有望升上80元水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20170815/00269_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170815%2F00269_001.html&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=90d9d2a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20170815/00269_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d62b147ba721500af9664aa88bb10df41a9ea3b3","tid":1933771,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"股王騰訊2017年首季業績勁省鏡，強勢到連「侵侵」出事都唔驚，港股跌百幾點都依然照破頂，今日科網爆小股災，股價都只係升少咗。從業績嚟睇，騰訊仲未到全盛時期，大膽咁講，買騰訊未來幾年都冇得輸！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20170518/56712117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170518%2F56712117&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=704beb2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170518%2F56712117&h=60c781ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20170518/56712117</a>"},{"pid":"d6a8e46f516625fa913339fb9a958fc10bdc4513","tid":1933771,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"香港股市踏進2018年「蒸蒸日上」，恒指昨日續創歷史新高，收報32,121點。今次港股升浪，其最大特點就是與國家發展緊密相連，內地經濟對香港股市提供了強大支撐，加上兩地融合互聯互通的大好形勢，締造了香港向前邁進的新局面。股市離不開經濟，經濟又離不開政通人和。特首林鄭月娥上任以來領導特區政府展現施政新風，貫徹「理財新哲學」，提出多項紓解民困怨氣、推動香港發展的新舉措，不僅有助社會改善經濟，更提振了市民對前景的信心，又為港股打下強心針。總結今次港股「大時代」的成功經驗，要將這一波態勢持續下去，港人更須憑藉「一國兩制」優勢，在國家支持及配合下去爭取、把握兩地融合的發展契機，支持特區政府集中精力處理好經濟民生，力排政爭干擾，更好乘搭國家發展的快車，不要錯過「大時代」下的新機遇。<br />\n<br />\n去年港股表現一鳴驚人，大幅上升約36%，領漲全球股市。在一眾內銀股以及騰訊、港交所帶動下，恒指日前更經歷了十年零三個月後的新高，港股進入另一個「大時代」，昨日更持續牛市升勢，連續兩日打破歷史最高點，成交超強近2,000億元。<br />\n<br />\n再次印證「國家好，香港更好」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/01/19/PL1801190001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2FPL1801190001.htm&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=3973829c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/01/19/PL1801190001.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6a4e01b38c485261de90237b002d65ce8714c0e3","tid":1933771,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"有無1478?"},{"pid":"a41f7c4c26553de34a2a02f89370196bb1b0f00f","tid":1933771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:22:05.000Z","msg":"新鴻基金融財富管理策略師溫傑，亦不建議短線投資者現時追入已爆升的騰訊及平保︰「騰訊＄400怎會是頂，仲有排升。平保下年會成紅底股，如果買了，可以繼續持有。如果看長線，打算放一年，當然還有上升潛力。但短線或中線的話，上升回報比例並不吸引。」散戶要自己睇位上路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/recommend/20171130/561119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Frecommend%2F20171130%2F561119&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=214770d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Frecommend%2F20171130%2F561119&h=a5de19cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/recommend/20171130/561119</a>"},{"pid":"9f15807d45a72468a1ec8c60118430686436509f","tid":1933771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a4e01b38c485261de90237b002d65ce8714c0e3","tid":1933771,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"有無1478?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:22:15.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"de018f56a3d820464a8ba8484b08efedc18ad829","tid":1933771,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f15807d45a72468a1ec8c60118430686436509f","tid":1933771,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a4e01b38c485261de90237b002d65ce8714c0e3","tid":1933771,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT